    bibo:startPage "193" ;
    bibo:volume "3821" ;
    dc:creator "Eow, Li-Xin" ;
    dc:date "2014" ;
    dc:title "Australian species of spore-feeding Thysanoptera in the genera Carientothrips and Nesothrips (Thysanoptera: Idolothripinae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4919974>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4920008>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4920094> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4919974>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1–9. Carientothrips species. Head: (1) mjobergi, (2) flavitibia, (3) tasmanica, (4) alienatus major male, (5) loisthus macropterae. Ventral eye surface: (6) alienatus, (7) miskoi, (8) flavitibia, (9) tasmanica." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4919974/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4920008>
    dc:description "FIGURES 56–61. Nesothrips species. Maxillary palps: (56) badius. Eye ventral surface: (57) propinquus. Antennal segments III–VIII: (58) yanchepi, (59) badius, (60) barrowi. Antennal segments II–VIII: (61) carveri." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4920008/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4920094>
    dc:description "FIGURES 62–68. Nesothrips species. Thoracic features and pelta: (62) coorongi, (63) rossi, (64) brigalowi, (65) barrowi. Pelta: (66) hemidiscus. Pronotum: (67) capricornis. Maxillary palps and mesopresternum: (68) propinquus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4920094/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

